text: Soaru Range also known as Sewori Range Coordinate geografiche per Sewori Range (montagne) in PAPUA NUOVA GUINEA is a mountain range in the Southern Highlands Province in central part of Papua New GuineaMap GA 7785 Publisher: Geoscience Australia (Australian Government) , 500 km north-west of Port Moresby is the nation's capitol. Soaru Range: Papua New Guinea National Geospatial- Intelligence Agency, Bethesda, MD, USA Populated places within range include Wembu.Wembu: Papua New Guinea National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency, Bethesda, MD, USA ==References== Category:Mountain ranges of Papua New Guinea
